{"lemma":"سَرِيعَةٍ","slug":"سَرِيعَةٍ","root":"س.ر.ع","root_slug":"س-ر-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/س-ر-ع","pos":"ADJ","pos_camel":"adj","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"سَرِيع","root":"سرع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":10},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["adj"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n19593"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B3%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B9%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8D"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"adj","gloss":"fast (capable of moving with speed), quick (moving with speed)"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/sa.riːʕ/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n19593","headword_ar":"سَرِيعٌ","root":"srE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick, expeditious, hasty, speedy, rapid, swift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleet;"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in course, tendency, action, speech, &c.;] (S, Msb, * TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariEN","text_ar":"سَرِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroEN","text_ar":"سَرْعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suraAEN","text_ar":"سُرَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the fem. is with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroEaAnu","text_ar":"سَرْعَانُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", of which the fem. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saroEaY","text_ar":"سَرْعَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musoriEN","text_ar":"مُسْرِعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) which signifies as above; (TA;) [and which also signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hastening, making haste,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"speeding;"},{"kind":"text","text":"] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"misoraEN","text_ar":"مِسْرَعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", also, signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c., ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariyE","text_ar":"سَرِيع"},{"kind":"text","text":",) to [do] good or evil: (K:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sryE","text_ar":"سريع"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroEaAnN","text_ar":"سُرْعَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siraAEN","text_ar":"سِرَاعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is [also a pl. of the same,] syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musoriEuwna","text_ar":"مُسْرِعُونَ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN sariyEN","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ سَرِيعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suraAEN","text_ar":"سُرَاعٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A quick, swift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleet, horse"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (IB:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HijorN suraAEapN","text_ar":"حِجْرٌ سُرَاعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariyEapN","text_ar":"سَرِيعَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a quick, swift,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fleet, mare"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AisoEa EalaY rijolika Als~aroEaY","text_ar":"اِسْعَ عَلَى رِجْلِكَ السَّرْعَى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Go thou quickly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"lit."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"go thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walk thou,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"run thou, upon thy quick,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"swift, leg"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Fr.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jaA='a saroEFA","text_ar":"جَا=ءَ سَرْعًا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariyEFA","text_ar":"سَرِيعًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"it, came quickly, hastily, speedily,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (TA.) And God is said [in the Kur ii. 198, &c.] to be"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariyEu AlHisaAbi","text_ar":"سَرِيعُ الحِسَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Quick in reckoning"},{"kind":"text","text":"], meaning that his reckoning will inevitably come to pass; or that one reckoning will not divert Him from another reckoning, nor one thing from another thing; or that his actions are quick, none of them being later than He desireth, because it is done without manual operation and without effort, so that He will reckon with mankind, after raising them from death and congregating them, in the twinkling of an eye, without numbering, or calculating: (K:) and [in like manner He is said in the same, chap. vi., last verse, to be]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sariyEu AlEiqaAbi","text_ar":"سَرِيعُ العِقَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"quick in punishing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (El-Mufradát, B.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A certain kind of going,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pace;"},{"kind":"text","text":"coupled with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"sunobukN","text_ar":"سُنْبُكٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", which signifies another kind thereof. (Ibn-Habeeb, TA.) ―         -b3-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Als~ariyEu","text_ar":"السَّرِيعُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The ninth metre"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baHor","text_ar":"بَحْر"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in prosody, in which each hemistich originally consisted of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musotafoEiluno musotafoEiluno mafoEuwlaAtu","text_ar":"مُسْتَفْعِلُنْ مُسْتَفْعِلُنْ مَفْعُولَاتُ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abuw sariyEK","text_ar":"اَبُو سَرِيعٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"The ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shrub called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Earofaj","text_ar":"عَرْفَج"},{"kind":"text","text":": or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fire that is therein."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K. [See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"zaHofapN","text_ar":"زَحْفَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A shoot,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"twig, that falls from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ba$aAm","text_ar":"بَشَام"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"tree of the balsam of Mekkeh"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"siroEaAnN","text_ar":"سِرْعَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"suroEaAnN","text_ar":"سُرْعَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.)"}],"source_refs":["K","IB"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}